author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Temasek Holdings Dissolves Share Stake In Marin Software, Takes Share Stake In Denali Therapeutics
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Temasek Holdings (Private) Ltd:
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD DISSOLVES SHARE STAKE IN MARIN SOFTWARE INC - SEC FILING
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD TAKES SHARE STAKE OF 4.4 MILLION SHARES IN DENALI THERAPEUTICS INC
* TEMASEK HOLDINGS (PRIVATE) LTD - CHANGE IN HOLDINGS ARE AS OF DEC 31, 2017 AND COMPARED WITH THE PREVIOUS QUARTER ENDED AS OF SEPT 30, 2017 Source text for quarter ended Dec 31, 2017: ( bit.ly/2EpcSgh ) Source text for quarter ended Sept 30, 2017: ( bit.ly/2yBi2ic )
